sections.text:
Normally a descent conversational agent for a particular domain requires tens of thousands of hand labeled conversational data or hand written rules. This is a major barrier when launching a conversation agent for a new domain. We will explore and demonstrate the effectiveness of the learning solution even when there is no hand written rules or hand labeled training data.
CCS Concepts •Information systems → Recommender systems;
Keywords Dialogue systems, recommendation systems, personal assistant, chat bot
